Practical training:
Create AWS Sandbox account under Helixiora org and document the process for Mina and future colleagues. You can spend up to 100 USD per month.
Create a wordpress site on AWS using Terraform and gihub
Configure monitoring alarms
Configure backup
Configure patching
Create dashboards for performance, cost, application and infrastructure uptime, security, and sustainability
Calculate the cost of the observability configured in tasks 3 and 6 as a percentage of the entire AWS cost
